<%= @tenant.dealership_name %> — this week's accountability digest

Hi <%= @tenant.gm_name %>,

<% if @digest.empty? %>
No submissions yet — we'll keep this digest going every week so nothing slips. As soon as your team starts setting up data collection, this email will start to fill in.
<% else %>
Here's where each responsibility stands:

<% @digest.rows.each do |row| %>
- <%= row.responsibility.tenant_question.deliverable.capitalize %>
  Owner:    <%= row.primary_email %>
  Status:   <%= case row.status
              when :pending_setup            then "Awaiting setup"
              when :pending_first_submission then "Pending first submission"
              when :on_time                  then "On time"
              when :late                     then "Late"
              when :overdue                  then "Overdue"
              else row.status.to_s
              end %>
  Next due: <%= row.next_due_at ? row.next_due_at.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%b %-d, %Y") : "—" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

Open the dashboard:
<%= @dashboard_url %>

This link is valid for 8 days. The next digest will include a fresh link.

— The Rogue team
